OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain or drizzle through
OL,7,Fthe evening. These easing after
OL,8,Fmidnight to become largely dry by
OL,9,Fdawn, although the odd spot of rain
OL,10,Fremaining possible in the east.
OL,11,FPerhaps some clear spells developing
OL,12,Ffurther west. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FAny overnight rain soon
OL,15,Fclearing. A dry and often cloudy
OL,16,Fmorning follows, with a few brighter
OL,17,Fspells. Cloud clearing in the
OL,18,Fafternoon to give longer sunny
OL,19,Fperiods. Very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
