OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,6,Ffog clearing, then dry and very mild
OL,7,Fwith warm sunny spells Wednesday.
OL,8,FBreezy with rain or showers Thursday.
OL,9,FLikely wet and windy at first Friday,
OL,10,Fthen cooler with showers.
